docs.text: torch2trt torch2trt is a PyTorch to TensorRT converter which utilizes the TensorRT Python API. The converter is Easy to use - Convert modules with a single function call torch2trt Easy to extend - Write your own layer converter in Python and register it with @tensorrt_converter If you find an issue, please let us know !
